early in the match. Belgium was eliminated from the rest of the
competition.
</P>
<P>
Leekens said, "We had a good beginning. But we have relaxed after
our goal. I do not know whether my players sit back mentally or the
Koreans played in a very relaxed way."
</P>
<P>
Luc Nilis scored the goal for Belgium in the seventh minute but Yoo
Sang Chul levelled the score in the 72nd minute.
</P>
<P>
Leekens added, "However, if we had won 1-0, we were out of the
competition as well."
</P>
<P>
He explained he substituted Enzo Scifo with Van der Elst in the
second half in order to have a more balanced team.
</P>
<P>
