<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, June 26 (Xinhua) -- Malaysian Prime Minister
Mahathir Mohamad said Friday his country did not need to ask for
economic bail-out from the International Monetary Fund (IMF)
because of several factors.
</P>
