offered to the general public via the audiovisual media in order
to expand the social influence of the art and provide economic
returns.
</P>
<P>
Priority should be placed on developing collective wisdom to
enhance the artistic level of Beijing Opera, said Li. He urged the
troupe to analyze the recent performances and take full advantage
of the troupe's collective advantages to stage even more high
quality plays.
</P>
<P>
A number of famous Beijing Opera masters expressed their
opinions during the meeting. 
