<HEADLINE> Brazilians Confident on Next Stage </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
PARIS, June 26 (Xinhua) -- Brazilian players are confident that
they can win the World Cup for a fifth time as the second round
competition starts on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
