for Spain, I am very disappointed about their elimination, since
they were one of the competition favorites." said Rivaldo who plays
for Spanish club Barcelona.
</P>
<P>
Free-kick expert Roberto Carlos said:"We are still 30 percent
short of being at our best. As for me, I feel that my game is
improving, as well as my shooting."
</P>
<P>
The Brazil-Chile match will be played at Parc des Princes
stadium on Saturday. 
