opposes the independence of Kosovo and admits the fact that Kosovo
is part of Yugoslavia.
</P>
<P>
Holbrooke made the remarks while meeting with a group of
Yugoslav journalists at the U.S. embassy in Belgrade. Beforehand,
he held talks with Yugoslav President Slobodan Milosevic on Kosovo.
</P>
