settlement of the crisis.
</P>
<P>
On his meeting Wednesday with members of the Kosovo Liberation
Army, the armed wing of the Kosovo ethnic Albanians who seek
independence of the province, Holbrooke noted that it was an
accidental and brief contact.
</P>
<P>
Kosovo has sunk into chaos since pro-independence ethnic
Albanians clashed with local Serb police in February. Several
hundred people have been killed since then. 
