<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, June 26 (Xinhua) -- Bangladesh will distribute 55,000
tons of rice to the destitute under the Vulnerable Group Feeding
(VGF) program in the coming 1998-99 fiscal year beginning July 1.
</P>
