distressed families under the VGF program and as food assistance
to 450,000 families under the Test Relief program in fiscal
1997-98, the report said.
</P>
<P>
With an area of 144,000 square kilometers, Bangladesh has a
population of 127 million, with nearly half of them living in
poverty. 
